You're seriously
going to make me die early, aren't you?

00:22:43.571 --> 00:22:45.072
- Get back down.
- Yes, sir.

00:22:48.909 --> 00:22:50.995
Sir, are you okay?

00:22:58.752 --> 00:22:59.753
How many did you take?

00:23:00.629 --> 00:23:03.299
You didn't count? You're asking for more.

00:23:03.757 --> 00:23:05.092
- Get back there.
- Yes, sir.

00:23:21.400 --> 00:23:22.484
Good-bye, sir.

00:23:27.197 --> 00:23:29.199
What are you looking at? Get back to work!

00:23:29.283 --> 00:23:30.492
Yes, sir.

00:23:34.246 --> 00:23:35.247
Where's Seokcheol?

