He can't come to work today
due to some other business.

00:23:38.125 --> 00:23:39.835
That punk really...

00:23:39.919 --> 00:23:42.880
Are you okay, sir?

00:23:49.511 --> 00:23:50.512
<i>So?</i>

00:23:50.596 --> 00:23:53.682
So, it was way past 9:00 p.m.

