You can imagine how dark it must've been.

00:23:56.977 --> 00:23:59.605
And kids weren't allowed to have phones
at that time.

00:23:59.688 --> 00:24:00.773
Right.

00:24:00.856 --> 00:24:03.692
I think Seokhee was around 10 then.

00:24:03.776 --> 00:24:05.778
Right, because I was in sixth grade.

00:24:05.861 --> 00:24:08.113
What was she up to until that hour?

00:24:08.197 --> 00:24:09.490
Who knows?

00:24:09.573 --> 00:24:12.534
Our father, in his pajamas,
went out on a bicycle to find her.

00:24:12.618 --> 00:24:14.620
I ran around the neighborhood too.

00:24:15.537 --> 00:24:18.582
It was so dark, there were no streetlamps.
I sensed it was serious.

00:24:18.666 --> 00:24:21.085
But then, from afar,

00:24:21.168 --> 00:24:23.379
I saw a little girl
approaching with someone.

00:24:23.462 --> 00:24:25.422
- Seokhee?
- Yes.

00:24:25.506 --> 00:24:26.507
With Seokkyung.

00:24:27.216 --> 00:24:28.217
Seokkyung found her?

00:24:28.300 --> 00:24:31.428
That's hard to tell.

00:24:31.512 --> 00:24:33.013
It's not that she found Seokhee.

00:24:33.097 --> 00:24:35.140
- Rather that Seokhee spotted her.
- What?

00:24:35.224 --> 00:24:38.185
She was wandering
on a ridge between rice paddies

00:24:38.268 --> 00:24:41.605
when she saw a cigarette light from afar.

00:24:41.689 --> 00:24:43.983
She figured it was someone
and dashed toward her.

00:24:44.066 --> 00:24:45.859
It turned out to be Seokkyung.

00:24:47.778 --> 00:24:48.821
Are you serious?

00:24:48.904 --> 00:24:52.783
As soon as Seokhee met her,
she called out to her and cried in relief.

00:24:52.866 --> 00:24:54.451
- Oh!
- Then, Seokkyung said,

00:24:54.535 --> 00:24:57.579
"If you tell Dad that I smoked,
I'll leave you here."

00:25:00.541 --> 00:25:02.376
- Your food is ready.
- Okay.

00:25:02.459 --> 00:25:03.794
That's insane.

00:25:03.877 --> 00:25:05.587
She's been like that
since childhood.

00:25:05.671 --> 00:25:07.297
Is this about Seokhee or Seokkyung?

00:25:08.424 --> 00:25:10.175
Both, I guess.

00:25:10.592 --> 00:25:12.136
- It looks good.
- Thanks.

00:25:12.761 --> 00:25:14.013
Thank you.

00:25:14.096 --> 00:25:15.556
How appetizing.

00:25:15.639 --> 00:25:17.391
- Enjoy.
- Thank you.

00:25:18.851 --> 00:25:20.394
SANGYEOL

00:25:20.477 --> 00:25:22.730
It looks amazing. How pretty.

00:25:22.813 --> 00:25:24.398
- Eat up.
- I'll cut it for you.

00:25:24.982 --> 00:25:28.235
<i>The person you called is unavailable--</i>

00:25:30.362 --> 00:25:31.447
That punk.

00:25:34.408 --> 00:25:36.577
Now you're ignoring me too?

00:25:38.495 --> 00:25:40.122
Goodness.

00:25:40.706 --> 00:25:41.874
Wait.

