My favorite white suit.
The one from my father.

00:25:54.970 --> 00:25:56.096
I'm having it dry-cleaned.

00:25:56.180 --> 00:25:57.639
What... Go get it now.

00:25:57.723 --> 00:25:59.183
Just wear something else.

